 Blackheart smiled. "Our goals here Tyrael are simple. Kill all remaining 
threats to the Tripredacus. The maximals are our main enemy but with what you 
say of Megatron still being alive, he too must be dealt with. Cybertorn is 
under our complete and total control. The maximals have fled to future earth 
where they now reside crippled. They have barely enough energon to survive, 
our victory is total. Except for Rodimus. We have learned from the past to 
never under estimate him. He must be destroyed."

--part1_e4.317cce09.2b1c08c4_boundary
